<h3>Re: Session Login Screen</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>then just launch the following command</p><div class="codebox"><pre><code>sudo systemctl disable lightdm</code></pre></div><p>this will disable the autostart of the lightdm display manager (login window)</p>
</div>
